#| "link=\"no\"]]&nbsp;▸ Account Settings**."
msgid ""
"Choose **[[!img lib/open-menu.png alt=\"Menu\" class=symbolic link=no]]</"
"span>&nbsp;▸ Account Settings** from the main window of *Thunderbird*."
msgstr ""
"Trieu **[[!img lib/open-menu.png alt=\"Menú\" class=\"symbolic\" "
"link=\"no\"]]&nbsp;▸ Paràmetres del compte**."

