"   If a site has no feed icon, right-click on the home or news page of the site\n"
"   and choose **View Page Source** in the shortcut menu. In the source of the\n"
"   page look for a link of type *application/rss+xml* or\n"
"   *application/atom+xml*. No all sites have a news feed.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "- Reading [[!wikipedia RSS]] and [[!wikipedia Atom_(Web_standard) desc=\"Atom\"]] feeds for news and blogs"
